BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 80 511 Td (3. Space tourism is already here - people can buy tickets to space!) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 80 489 Td (4. Scientists are developing faster propulsion systems for deep space) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 80 472 Td (   travel.) Tj ET
