BT 0.1 g /F2 13 Tf 72 580 Td (MIND-BLOWING FACTS:) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 80 555 Td (1. There are billions of potentially habitable planets in our galaxy) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 80 538 Td (   alone.) Tj ET
