BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 80 311 Td (9. In 2020, a possible biosignature was detected in Venus's atmosphere.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 80 289 Td (10. Finding even microbial alien life would be the biggest discovery in) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 80 272 Td (   human history!) Tj ET

